<STARTDOC>
macro(def(macroname)(nrofargs)(redefinition))
(Defines tt(macroname) as a macro, having tt(nrofargs) arguments, and
expanding to tt(redefinition). This macro is a shorthand for
tt(DEFINEMACRO).) An error occurs when the macro is already defined. Use
tt(redef()) to unconditionally define or redefine a macro.
<>

DEFINEMACRO(def)(3)(\
    DEFINEMACRO(ARG1)(ARG2)(ARG3)\
)

